- fixato dns1 e dns2 per rispondere anche su google.se impostavo come dns server i nostri locali i dns esterni non venivano pi√π risolto, creando 2000 problemi.
ho aggiunto questo fix nella configurazione di bind:
  forwarders {
                8.8.8.8;
                8.8.4.4;
        };


microk8s kubectl apply -f https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ansible/awx-operator/devel/deploy/awx-operator.yaml


tee awxconfig.yaml<<EOF
---
apiVersion: awx.ansible.com/v1beta1
kind: AWX
metadata:
  annotations:
    kubernetes.io/ingress.class: nginx
  name: awx
  namespace: default
spec:
  tower_create_preload_data: true
  tower_hostname: awx-office.gesuvive
  tower_image_pull_policy: IfNotPresent
  tower_ingress_tls_secret: awx-office-com-tls
  tower_ingress_type: Ingress
EOF
kubectl apply -f awxconfig.yaml



